Package: mvgb
Title: Multivariate Probabilities of Scale Mixtures of Multivariate Normal Distributions via the Genz and Bretz (2002) QRSVN Method
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Alan", "Genz", role="aut", comment=c("wrote mvtdstpack.f")),
      person("Bruce", "Swihart", 
             role = c("aut", "cre"), 
             email="bruce.swihart@gmail.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4216-9942")
             ))
Description: Generates multivariate student-t probabilities using the QRSVN
    algorithm as detailed in Genz and Bretz (2002) <DOI:10.1198/106186002394>
    but by sampling gamma variates not chi/sqrt(nu).
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0),
  mvtnorm
